  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Higher model risk drives stricter credibility requirements; Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed and all 13 credibility factors are fully assessed with achieved levels meeting or exceeding required levels. Full 13-factor assessment: all factors assessed, all with achieved levels at or above required levels. Decision: Accepted.",
