      "type": "OperatingEnvelope",
      "name": "COU2 operating envelope — VAD hemolysis CFD",
      "description": "Defined operating envelope for the VAD hemolysis CFD model: flow rate 2–8 L/min (nominal 5 L/min), rotational speed 2000–6000 RPM (nominal 3500 RPM), differential pressure head 60–120 mmHg, fluid temperature 36–38 °C, hematocrit 35–45%, blood viscosity 0.0030–0.0045 Pa·s, impeller tip diameter 30–55 mm, gap clearance 50–300 µm. Five operating points (Q, N) are evaluated: (2 L/min, 2500 RPM), (3.5 L/min, 3000 RPM), (5 L/min, 3500 RPM), (6.5 L/min, 4000 RPM), (8 L/min, 4500 RPM)."
    }
  },
